  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf - \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka's fuel crisis - Kanzana Wijesekera talks with Qatari energy officials",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kansana Wijesekera has held discussions with key officials in Qatar's energy sector on resolving the fuel crisis in Sri Lanka.",
        "Chad Sheridan, Minister of State for Energy and Head of Qatar Energy and Chief Executive, met with Sheridan al-Kabi today.",
        "He added that discussions were held on supplying petroleum products, liquefied petroleum gas (LPG) and liquefied natural gas (LNG) to Sri Lanka to overcome the fuel crisis.",
        "The Minister also said that the discussion was aimed at overcoming Sri Lanka's energy crisis with the assistance of the Qatar Energy and Qatar Development Fund.",
        "In this context, it is noteworthy that Minister Kanchana Wijesekera accompanied by Environment Minister Nasir Ahmed left for Qatar this morning."
      ],
